  "detailed_description": "Locked inside a mental hospital, your mission is to simply, escape.<br><br>This game is very difficult, you get 1 life, 1 hp, limited time & limited ammo, when you die, you start from the beginning.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Different kind of enemies, ranged and melee.<br></li><li> Bosses<br></li><li> Limited ammo<br></li><li> Limited time<br></li><li> No checkpoints, you die, you reset.<br></li><li> 3 Difficulty levels<br></li><li> Multiplayer support, play with a friend (2 player coop)<br></li><li> Time & Score Leaderboards</li></ul>",
